name: Smile
description:
NEW ANIMATED SERIES *GODK:LLERS* 
Follow the story of #7, a 12-year-old boy created to be the ultimate weapon against the Gods! He and his estranged siblings embark on an ethereal journey to stop a madman from awakening an ancient artifact and find freedom from their destructive origins.

This smiley face collection originates from #7's hoodie. The smile allows 7 to face dangerous enemies and adversity despite his timid nature.
